title: VA - Every Summer Has A Story (2013)
description:
Escape from rush hour and cut loose from the stressful, everyday life- with a selection of chill out and deep house tracks.Every Summer Has A Story perseveres to relax your mind with some of the best down tempo cuts and loungy tracks. With Every Summer Has A Story, Body Condition takes you to a place where everything but the music disappears. A true getaway with soothing vocals, deep melodic twists, refined beats and lush lounge productions from the hands of Rodg, Rasmus Dupont, Man In A Room, Giuseppe Favia, Ray Saul and Ruben de Ronde.
